      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example is mechanically sound with a documented Double-VANOS service and reinforced rear subframe mounting points to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The factory limited-slip differential provides exceptional traction out of corners, complemented by a suspension setup that retains its communicative feedback and damping characteristics. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the powertrain remains robust with a smooth torque curve and a redline that holds true to its 8,000 RPM pedigree. Recent maintenance includes a valve adjustment and fresh bushings, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning purist.",
